WEBVTT

00:00.967 --> 00:04.232
Michael, I'm picking up two men on
the ridge above you. One has a rifle.

00:04.304 --> 00:07.034
Stephanie, get inside! Go!

00:07.107 --> 00:09.041
KITT, cover us!

00:11.077 --> 00:13.602
Our conspiracy case
rests on your testimony.

00:13.680 --> 00:16.877
No matter what happens,
you stay with KITT.

00:19.119 --> 00:22.782
But you just seem so familiar to
me... Your voice, the way you move.

00:24.324 --> 00:27.191
They're gonna try and take her out of the
picture before she gets to the grand jury.

00:29.000 --> 00:35.074
